2704 Virginia Register of Regulations 2590 CUMULATIVE TABLE OF VIRGINIA ADMINISTRATIVE CODE SECTIONS ADOPTED, AMENDED, OR REPEALED The table printed below lists regulation sections, by Virginia Administrative Code (VAC) title, that have been amended, added or repealed in the Virginia Register since the regulations were originally published or last supplemented in VAC (the Spring 2000 VAC Supplement includes final regulations published through Virginia Register Volume 16, Issue 11, dated February 14, 2000).
Emergency regulations, if any, are listed, followed by the designation "emer," and errata pertaining to final regulations are listed.
Proposed regulations are not listed here.
The table lists the sections in numerical order and shows action taken, the volume, issue and page number where the section appeared, and the effective date of the section.
