Volume 16, Issue 21 2619 "Virginia Targeted Jobs Grant Program" or "VTJG" means the program established in a grant paid to an employer in accordance with Ã¯Â¿Â½ 63.1-25.3 of the Code of Virginia which pays a grant to employers who hire qualified participants in the Virginia Initiative for Employment not Welfare Program.
